               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾāmmǝra ʾIyasus “Miracles of Jesus” (fols. 2ra-52vb)&#xD; I-1)
                     ʾƎsaggǝd la-malakotǝka... “I worship Thy Godhead…” (fols. 2ra-4rb)&#xD; I-2)
                     Introduction (fols. 5ra-16rb)&#xD; - On John the Evangelist as the author of
                     the book; on the creation and the fall of the angels (fols. 5ra-10ra)&#xD; -
                     Story of the family of Adam (fols. 10ra-16rb)&#xD; I-3) Taʾāmmǝra ʾIyasus
                     “Miracles of Jesus”: 15 miracles (fols. 16rb-52vb), incomplete [continuation of
                     the text is in <ref type="mss" corresp="ESamm006">AMM-006</ref>]&#xD; &#xD; Additio 1.</summary>
